latestIgtvVideos.title: Be the smart citizen, you aspire everyone else to be.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Knowing about the precautionary measures isn't enough. The question boils down to us. Are we adhering to the precautions? Taking care of ourselves and others around?

My message to everyone out there, including myself is Before we vent or rant about what's happening around, it's important to reflect upon our actions and stay accountable about the same.

I'd like to extend immense amount of gratitude to @missvizag2021 @vizagcelebritiess @hcgcancercentrevizag @foxey_photography @hellovizag.online @ajayagarwal4493  all the organisations and individuals involved with Miss Vizag 2021 to promote and enable the initiative of Beauty with a Cause.

Stay Home, Stay Safe!
#missvizag2021 #covidawareness

latestPosts.caption:
Who said dreams don’t come true?

My first hoarding is finally up, and there’s no turning back now! In the middle of the shoot, I stepped out to see this, and I could hardly believe it. It’s real—dreams do come true, manifestation is powerful, and hard work truly pays off. My heart is full ♥️♥️♥️

To all the young girls out there: keep dreaming big, because I’m rooting for you every step of the way! 

Here’s to chasing even bigger dreams 🥂

Love & Gratitude to the ones who’ve always been cheering for me, you know who you are ♥️✨

All credits to @rajputhri.official @vinayaghar_photography @appu_the_make_up_touch  for making this happen 👊🏻☀️💯💪🏻

Sarees are my forever mooood! ✨ 

2024 has been blissful with all the weddings I attended 😇🫶🏻

#love #explore #fyp #explorefyp #ootd #grwm #travel #traveldiaries #fits #wedding #weddingseason

Day 1/365 🫶🏻 

A promise to myself: this year will be one of growth and solitude! Yeh dastan, manzoor hai hume 😇♥️

I plan to document every single day and make the most of it, whether it’s on social media or not. Grateful for all the energies that shaped 2024. Nothing but love for everyone who made it special, you know who you are ♥️💯✨

#ajibdastanhaiyeh #love #gratitude
